🗺️ Roadmap & Governance
OLOS is managed by the OLOS Foundation, a neutral non-profit entity dedicated exclusively to standard maintenance, security audits, and open-source tooling.
 * Phase 1: Foundation & White Paper (Q3–Q4 2026) — Foundation establishment & founding merchant anchor cohort recruitment.
 * Phase 2: Protocol Specification (Q4 2026–Q2 2027) — Release of technical specifications, SDKs, and Gateway reference builds.
 * Phase 3: Devnet & Sandbox (Q2–Q3 2027) — Sandbox deployment for third-party developer testing.
 * Phase 4: Private Beta Consortia (Q3–Q4 2027) — Pilot implementations with founding merchant cohort.
 * Phase 5: Public Testnet (Q4 2027–Q2 2028) — Node operator bootstrapping and governance activation.
 * Phase 6: Mainnet Soft Launch (Q2–Q4 2028) — Live production deployment on banking settlement rails.
